OL,3,CChristmas inside time capsule house
OL,4,Cleft untouched since 1920s
OL,6,FThe owners of a house which has
OL,7,Fremained largely untouched since the
OL,8,F1920s will give the public the chance
OL,9,Fto experience Christmas as it would
OL,10,Fhave been celebrated a century ago.
OL,12,F"Mr Straw's House" - at number 7 Blyth
OL,13,FGrove in Worksop, Nottinghamshire -
OL,14,Fhas been virtually unchanged since the
OL,15,FStraw family moved there in 1923.
OL,17,FMany of their belongings, including
OL,18,Fclothes and collectibles, are still in
OL,19,Fsitu.
