OL,3,CChristmas inside time capsule house
OL,4,Cleft untouched since 1920s
OL,6,FWhen Mrs Straw died in 1939, the
OL,7,Fcouple's sons William and Walter
OL,8,Foccupied the house and settled into a
OL,9,Fway of life that remained largely
OL,10,Funchanged for the next 40 years.
OL,12,FMrs Straw's recipe collection is a
OL,13,Frelic of its time, including
OL,14,Finstructions for making apple pudding,
OL,15,Fapple jelly and apple chutney.
