OL,3,CChristmas inside time capsule house
OL,4,Cleft untouched since 1920s
OL,6,FFor more than 60 years, William and
OL,7,FWalter threw little away and chose to
OL,8,Feschew many modern comforts. Walter
OL,9,Fdied in 1976. When William died 14
OL,10,Fyears later, he left the contents of
OL,11,Fthe house to the National Trust, who
OL,12,Fthen purchased the building to display
OL,13,Fthe house as it had been left by the
OL,14,Fbrothers.
OL,16,FThe property is usually closed during
OL,17,Fthe winter, but this year it will open
OL,18,Fon Thursdays and Fridays between 21
OL,19,FNovember and 20 December.
